WEBVTT

00:00:00.379 --> 00:00:04.219
Good morning, family. How are you all doing today? Praise the Lord.

00:00:04.220 --> 00:00:15.930
I had a dream last night, and the Lord spoke to me, warning me to warn you all about watching your children during the holiday season.

00:00:15.931 --> 00:00:30.879
When you're going out shopping, don't get distracted. If you take them into a mall or a major retail store, don't get distracted with your surroundings.

00:00:30.880 --> 00:00:46.523
I saw that there was a plan while people were distracted; they had children wandering around, going off from them a little bit to look at presents or something from the store.

00:00:46.524 --> 00:00:53.519
These were younger kids, probably ten years old and younger.

00:00:53.520 --> 00:01:06.287
I saw men watching the children and watching the parents secretly, as if they didn't know they were being followed.

00:01:06.288 --> 00:01:21.041
These mothers were distracted with all the other kids. If you had two or three kids with you, you would be distracted with shopping because the places were full of people.

00:01:21.042 --> 00:01:38.578
As the other kid would wander off, I saw the men assigned to grab these children for bad intentions. This is something we can pray against today.

00:01:38.579 --> 00:01:53.590
I've seen in the comments where people ask, "Where did the 350,000 kids go?"After my son brought that up, I had this dream.

00:01:53.591 --> 00:02:00.447
I know when the Lord's speaking to me because I wake up and can't stop thinking about it all day; it's stirring in my spirit.

00:02:00.448 --> 00:02:10.863
I believe the Lord is warning me to warn you all so that you are on guard.

00:02:10.864 --> 00:02:21.238
I've warned you about being in public places already because of people doing stupid things with mass shootings and big events.

00:02:21.239 --> 00:02:38.474
I am praying over the Macy's Thanksgiving Day Parade next week, Rockin'New Year's Eve, Atlanta—because He showed me Atlanta—the shopping malls, and events in general because it's a very active time of year.

00:02:38.475 --> 00:02:45.344
This was just another thing the Lord brought up to tell people: watch your children.

00:02:45.345 --> 00:02:57.308
Do not walk in fear; it's not a call to fear, but a call to prayer so that your antenna is up.

00:02:57.309 --> 00:03:03.743
Keep your antennas up because the enemy has a plan all the time to kill, steal, and destroy.

00:03:03.744 --> 00:03:13.324
We pray against those plans so that people are watching their kids and their surroundings when they go shopping.

00:03:13.325 --> 00:03:18.714
It's an exciting time, and people are not paying attention because they are looking at sales.

00:03:18.715 --> 00:03:34.856
I wanted to shed some light on an enemy plan to kidnap children and take them into slavery.

00:03:34.857 --> 00:03:48.477
I've been praying over the war, interceding for what I believe would be an acceleration of what I've seen coming.

00:03:48.478 --> 00:04:00.202
I believe the Lord wants to give us a window of extended grace and favor, turning things around with the economy.

00:04:00.203 --> 00:04:11.211
I've told you all about the attack against the economy and the house of cards falling.

00:04:11.212 --> 00:04:23.772
My son is making a video for you right now, and this was the Antichrist flag that the Lord showed me when I went to tribulation with Jesus.

00:04:23.773 --> 00:04:45.998
This is what the Antichrist will raise up and put on all the buildings whenever he is ruling. He makes you take down your country's flag and put up his.

00:04:45.999 --> 00:04:53.563
I tried to the best of my ability to remember the five stars representing the five pillars of Islam.

00:04:53.564 --> 00:05:25.906
It is very interesting, like the UN logo, but this is the old Afghan flag from the 2000s.

00:05:25.907 --> 00:05:48.281
After Afghanistan fell, it was the Northern Alliance flag that this actually looks like. My son made this, and it came right out of my spirit.

00:05:48.282 --> 00:06:26.729
When somebody said it looked like the Northern Afghanistan Alliance flag, I was like, "What?"I bring all this up to rehash it because there are a lot of new faces here. I'm grateful for every single one of you subscribing.

00:06:26.730 --> 00:06:57.900
I was out in the garage praying, and I heard the Lord tell me, "Trump will be known as a wartime president."I thought, "Well, that's not good."I asked the Lord for the direction of 2025.

00:06:57.901 --> 00:07:06.448
Are we going to have a major crash or see the house of cards fall?

00:07:06.449 --> 00:07:24.066
I was praying over the plague I've seen coming, the economy, and the new digital platform they're birthing.

00:07:24.067 --> 00:07:39.984
The Lord showed me key people in NATO were trying to stir up this war because Trump was going to try to pull out completely and not fund the Ukrainian thing.

00:07:39.985 --> 00:08:02.918
The Lord showed me Trump would try to strong-arm Putin, but the Lord said, "You will not be able to strong-arm Putin this way."He'll have to handle him with caution because things have escalated rapidly.

00:08:02.919 --> 00:08:29.325
We have to pray he has supernatural wisdom on how to walk around landmines because you're dealing with an aggressive enemy that is like a wounded animal. This war has been going on for four years.

00:08:29.326 --> 00:08:59.178
Emmanuel Macron has been kind of quiet since President Trump was announced, but I told you the UK would be involved, supplying missiles and trying to provoke a major World War III by sending these long-range weapons.

00:08:59.179 --> 00:09:07.231
Biden is going alongside it, saying they're innocent while giving these weapons.

00:09:07.232 --> 00:09:53.951
They're saying if you do this, we're going to use weapons we've never used before—weapons of mass destruction, major artillery.

00:09:53.952 --> 00:10:08.186
Old Cold War alliances are trying to stir up again. The Lord showed me they would try to bring down the dollar through BRICS and other things.

00:10:08.187 --> 00:10:23.150
They were watching to see how President Trump or Kamala Harris would handle the next phases because they had a plan both ways.

00:10:23.151 --> 00:10:41.707
I believe it's through an acceleration of war. The Lord told me there are very sobering days ahead.

00:10:41.707 --> 00:11:00.537
How the body of Christ will get through this is by being filled with the Holy Spirit.

00:11:00.538 --> 00:11:51.651
In these last days, you will have to maintain a spirit of joy and keep yourself under the umbrella of His protection, understanding your covenant and walking in your authority in Psalm 91 and Psalm 23.

00:11:51.652 --> 00:12:01.352
I believe with all my heart we will see the plague; it will come and do what the Bible said: plagues and pestilences.

00:12:01.353 --> 00:12:31.766
Do we fear it? No, but we are here for the birthing pains. As labor pains upon a woman, they get more intense.

00:12:31.767 --> 00:12:54.976
He said He would always provide for and take care of His beloved. We walk with wisdom and pray over what He tells us.

00:12:54.977 --> 00:13:04.379
The body of Christ must rise up more than ever and take authority so that the devil does not get a foothold.

00:13:04.380 --> 00:13:34.339
The Lord told me, "When the election's over is not when this starts; it's when you put your foot on the gas even harder, interceding for what's coming."The enemy has a plan, and we are to put a kink in his hose.

00:13:34.340 --> 00:13:45.010
I have a book right here called "The Ultimate Voice"by Oral Roberts. Diana is reading with me now.

00:13:45.011 --> 00:13:51.874
She's been helping me answer emails; it's been crazy, hasn't it, babe?

00:13:51.875 --> 00:14:28.682
This was the last book Oral Roberts ever wrote in his 90s, and there are nuggets in here on how to hear the voice of the Lord for yourself.

00:14:28.683 --> 00:14:35.898
You don't need a prophet to hear about investments or where you're supposed to live.

00:14:35.899 --> 00:14:49.719
You have the Holy Spirit inside you. Reading books like this fans the flame. Diana, read that passage.

00:14:49.720 --> 00:15:10.792
[Diana reads]: "God will call you to become an extension to others of what He has done in your life.

00:15:10.793 --> 00:15:21.710
The area of your life that God heals is very likely the area of service He wants you to extend to others.

00:15:21.711 --> 00:15:27.144
The person who has been healed emotionally from abuse becomes a healer to those who are abused.

00:15:27.145 --> 00:15:54.723
The person who has been healed physically becomes a nurse or physician.

00:15:54.724 --> 00:16:03.215
No person can minister God’s love to another person beyond his level of personal experience.

00:16:03.216 --> 00:16:18.713
To minister God’s love, the other person must know that you have been where he is.

00:16:18.714 --> 00:16:35.514
You will find it difficult to believe for others to have a miracle unless you have experienced that miracle in your own life.

00:16:35.515 --> 00:16:43.959
Once you have experienced miracles, it is easy to believe for miracles in the lives of others.

00:16:43.960 --> 00:17:04.011
I have been a far more compassionate evangelist because I know what it means to have been sick.

00:17:04.012 --> 00:17:26.148
What He has done in you, He likely desires to do through you."Do you see that? What have you come through in your life?

00:17:26.149 --> 00:17:39.954
God will use that pain to help someone else who is walking through it right now because you have compassion for it.

00:17:39.955 --> 00:18:07.879
We have more compassion for people with special needs. Every single time I see them, it makes me want to weep.

00:18:07.880 --> 00:18:13.072
When someone has walked through cancer, they have more compassion.

00:18:13.073 --> 00:18:45.824
When we went to Billy Burke, he said you will have an anointing for women that have children with special needs in the womb—with Down syndrome and things like that—because we've walked through that valley of the shadow of death.

00:18:45.825 --> 00:19:28.313
Diana and I stand with you for your kids and special needs children.

00:19:28.314 --> 00:19:36.262
We're going to pray over your children, this war, and protection as you go to the malls.

00:19:36.263 --> 00:19:59.621
Be like a military scout watching the wall; my kids aren't leaving my side.

00:19:59.622 --> 00:20:05.213
Father, I thank You for every person represented here today.

00:20:05.214 --> 00:20:16.259
