00:20:37.928 --> 00:21:11.600
You said it would be better to have never been born or have a millstone thrown around your neck and be dragged to the bottom of the ocean if you lay hands on one of these little children.

00:21:11.601 --> 00:21:31.639
Show the authorities, the Trump administration—when they come into power, they will find every single one of them and bring them to safety. Let all hidden things be revealed.

00:21:31.640 --> 00:22:20.248
